item.description:
@archerer98 wrote:

If your not going to help then get out of here,no matter how nooby the question is they still deserve help.

Download the moparscape 3.2 client if you have not already then open it up and after it loads type in a username and pass then go to the "help tab at the top of the client and click on “server status” and pick a server you want to join thats on and type in the ip where it asks for the ip under username and pass
